Data attribution

This repository contains code only. The underlying datasets are not included
and must be obtained directly from their respective providers. When using or
citing this work, please also cite the original data sources:

Badan Informasi Geospasial (BIG). BATAS_WILAYAH [MapServer]. 2025.
  https://geoservices.big.go.id/rbi/rest/services/BATASWILAYAH/BATAS_WILAYAH/MapServer

Badan Pusat Statistik (BPS). Produk Domestik Regional Bruto. https://www.bps.go.id/

Didan, K. (2021). MODIS/Terra Vegetation Indices 16-Day L3 Global 500m SIN
  Grid V061. NASA EOSDIS Land Processes DAAC.
  https://doi.org/10.5067/MODIS/MOD13A1.061

Friedl, M. and Sulla-Menashe, D. (2022). MODIS/Terra+Aqua Land Cover Type Yearly
  L3 Global 500m SIN Grid V061. NASA EOSDIS Land Processes DAAC.
  https://doi.org/10.5067/MODIS/MCD12Q1.061

NASA Ocean Biology Processing Group (2022). MODIS-Aqua Level-3 Chlorophyll-a
  Data (2002–2024), Version R2022.0. NASA Ocean Biology DAAC.
  https://oceandata.sci.gsfc.nasa.gov/l3/

GEBCO Compilation Group (2025). GEBCO 2025 Grid.
  https://doi.org/10.5285/37c52e96-24ea-67ce-e063-7086abc05f29

Hansen, M. C., et al. (2013). High-Resolution Global Maps of 21st-Century
  Forest Cover Change. Science, 342, 850–853. Data (CC BY 4.0):
  https://glad.earthengine.app/view/global-forest-change

Li, X., Zhou, Y., Zhao, M., & Zhao, X. (2020). Harmonization of DMSP and
  VIIRS Nighttime Light Data from 1992–2024 at the Global Scale (Version 10).
  figshare (CC BY 4.0). https://doi.org/10.6084/m9.figshare.9828827.v10
